# SPA fallback — serve index.html for all client-side routes
# CF Pages serves static files before evaluating these rules, so assets are unaffected.
# Exact-match rules without trailing slash are unreliable on CF Pages; /* catches all SPA paths.
/for/*      /index.html  200
/lp         /index.html  200
/lp/        /index.html  200
/thank-you  /index.html  200
/thank-you/ /index.html  200
/*          /index.html  200
